Definition: experiencing or showing sorrow or unhappiness
Example: feeling sad because his dog had died; Better by far that you should forget and smile / Than that you should remember and be sad- Christina Rossetti
Synonyms: noun, state, sadness, feeling, GLAD, experiencing, or, showing, sorrow, unhappiness, sad, because, his, dog, had, died, Better, by, far, that, you, should, forget, and, smile, Than, remember, be, -, Christina, Rossetti
Category: adj.all
